"Maxima session showing the chaotic dynamics of the Duffing oscillator. The "
"differential equation of the forced oscillator are solved with Maxima. Plots "
"of the trajectory, the phase space of the oscillator and the corresponding "
"Poincaré map are done with LabPlot:"
